  "A phone manufacturer surveys 600 customers about phone brand (Brand A, Brand B) and satisfaction (Satisfied, Neutral, Dissatisfied). Brand A: Satisfied=180, Neutral=60, Dissatisfied=60. Brand B: Satisfied=120, Neutral=90, Dissatisfied=90. Is there an association between brand and satisfaction?": "",
